{"tid":1271001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"惡法未撤回 林鄭未下台 今日再上街","createTime":"2019-07-01T04:30:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T05:31:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c9800df9eaaa043a6d934174b25ee660c4602c2a","tid":1271001,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T04:30:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190701/20717756\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190701%2F20717756&d=IJ4Nzxd4hLWYFZk0XL5Pga3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=8255fa8f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190701%2F20717756&h=0ecb4069\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190701/20717756</a><br />\n<br />\n惡法未撤回 林鄭未下台<br />\n今日再上街<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190701/large/a0101a1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190701%2Flarge%2Fa0101a1.gif&h=5d88bf82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港人經歷回歸以來最傷感的6月，我們被催淚彈、胡椒噴霧熏得淚流滿面，因失去一個又一個戰友而痛不欲生；這也是最令人振奮的6月，103萬人一同為抗惡法走上街頭，200萬＋1人拒絕收貨堅持向政府怒吼，一日內成功眾籌600萬元，讓世界聽得見我們的呼喚。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：撐警大集會 變「犯罪樂園」<br />\n<br />\n不過，這個沒有人民授權的林鄭月娥政府只肯敷衍道歉、龜縮拖延，堅拒問責下台、撤回修例、撤銷暴動定性。面對冥頑不靈的政權，我們沒有放棄的餘地，也沒有放軟腳步的權利。<br />\n<br />\n走過兩次反送中大遊行的長者今日堅決再上街，為支持下一代爭取應有的權利；70後中年怒斥林鄭政府誠信破產，再一次以腳步拆穿政府謊言；80後打工仔雖然失望但未絕望，因深信走下去才看得見希望；90後女生認為「係香港人就應該行出嚟，因為唔行出嚟對唔住自己」；00後學生踏出人生第一個7.1遊行，只希望盡自己能力做好本份。<br />\n<br />\n民陣指，林鄭未下台，惡法未撤回，一日政權未回應五大訴求，香港人仍會共同進退。我們也許疲憊，但不能停下來；我們也許心痛，但拭乾眼淚便要再上路，一起走下去，一個都不能少，7.1，上街去。<br />\n<br />\n記者：鍾雅宜 麥卓溢 凌懿君<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：早場冷清 僅20人到警總支持<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190701/large/a0101b1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190701%2Flarge%2Fa0101b1.gif&h=64058347&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190701/large/a0101c1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190701%2Flarge%2Fa0101c1.gif&h=737e9704&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190701/large/a0101d1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190701%2Flarge%2Fa0101d1.gif&h=171ffacd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190701/large/a0101e1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190701%2Flarge%2Fa0101e1.gif&h=0064ee8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190701/large/a0101f1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190701%2Flarge%2Fa0101f1.gif&h=39e9d24b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190701/large/a0101g1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190701%2Flarge%2Fa0101g1.gif&h=2e92c608&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190701/large/a0101h1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190701%2Flarge%2Fa0101h1.gif&h=f12b09d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190701/large/a0101i1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190701%2Flarge%2Fa0101i1.gif&h=e6501d9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190701/large/a0101j1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190701%2Flarge%2Fa0101j1.gif&h=dfdd215f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190701/large/a0101k1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190701%2Flarge%2Fa0101k1.gif&h=c8a6351c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190701/large/a0101l1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190701%2Flarge%2Fa0101l1.gif&h=acc758d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n撐警大集會 變「犯罪樂園」<br />\n<br />\n撐警大集會 變「犯罪樂園」<br />\n早場冷清 僅20人到警總支持<br />\n黑社會吹雞撐警爆衝突<br />\n記協譴責危害記者安全<br />\n會展「戒嚴」首取消公眾觀禮<br />\n斥封館大陣仗 參展商索償<br />\n高智晟妻今與港人同行<br />\n流亡學運領袖周鋒鎖遭拒入境<br />\n反自動當選 做選民懲罰建制<br />\n葉劉誣衊變臉 李柱銘邀對質<br />\n胡志偉：777企硬恐擦槍走火<br />\n林鄭任內樓價飆17%專家：房策冇得救<br />\n學者、AI公司合作計遊行人數<br />\n「場仗未打完 不可再少一人」<br />\n女文員ifc墮橋亡 fb：盼看到港人勝利<br />\n死者父哭訴：我個女好乖<br />\n專家籲勿互傳消息「放負」<br />\n西環集中營：林鄭擺京上枱防建制作反<br />\n法改會92年倡修例警懶理縱容濫暴<br />\n大狀促立法規管截查程序<br />\n建議僅半數落實 修例最長17年<br />\n逆權六月<br />\n沒有大台的抗爭<br />\n完全抗爭手冊<br />\n血債票償"},{"pid":"08a45d1e4204aec04a4cf52a344b97414322504b","tid":1271001,"uid":192334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T04:38:05.000Z","msg":"🕝🌂🥽⛑🎗📱❤️💧🚯😘"},{"pid":"322b6880c7a5fe19b1660005e20b927c4fce515e","tid":1271001,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T04:38:49.000Z","msg":"撤回惡法 林鄭下台<br />\n重啟政改 釋放所有政治犯 <br />\n撤銷暴動定性 徹查6.12鎮壓"},{"pid":"a04a9589730656d0932a5722700f356a48e6d1ad","tid":1271001,"uid":25558,"like":0,"